## 2. File Path Format

The file paths injected into the message are relative paths from the working directory. For example, if the cwd is `/home/user/project` and a file is uploaded to `/home/user/project/.dork/.temp/uploads/abc12345-screenshot.png`, the injected text would be:

```
Please read the following uploaded file:
- .dork/.temp/uploads/abc12345-screenshot.png

<user's message>
```

For multiple files:

```
