- .dork/.temp/uploads/abc12345-screenshot.png
- .dork/.temp/uploads/def67890-data.csv

<user's message>
```

This format allows the Claude Code agent to read the files using its existing filesystem tools (`Read`, `cat`, etc.) since the paths are relative to the session's working directory.

